<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1>.::Bem-Vindo::.</h1>
<p>O sistema demonstra à associações entre father(pai), children(filho) e com com Occupation(que é a profissão do pai)</p>

<h2>Fathers</h2>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>CPF</th>
      <th>E-mail</th>
      <th colspan="3"></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @fathers.each do |father| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= father.name %></td>
        <td><%= father.cpf %></td>
        <td><%= father.email %></td>
        <td><%= father.email %></td>
        <td><%= father.occupation.description %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Show', father %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_father_path(father) %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', father, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<br>

<%= link_to 'New Father', new_father_path %> |
<%= link_to 'Go Children', children_path %> |
<%= link_to 'Go Occupation', occupations_path %>
